       <narrative xml:lang="EN">Target 1.1:
b) 25 procured hydro-meteorological stations to be installed in designated locations
Target 1.2:
Enhanced modelling tools and technologies for the strategic flood risk assessment in DRB based on EUFD, including: 
a)	Spatial Data Initiative and data management system; 
b)	Detailed topographic surveys and data for the Crn Drim in Macedonia - Procurement of LiDAR Digital Elevation Models (DEM) data completed
c)	Detailed hydrological and hydraulic modelling for the Crn Drim in Macedonia and high resolution flood hazard inundation maps 
d)	Numerical high-level basin-wide hydrological and hydraulic models of the DRB integrating detailed area-based modeling developed under AF, GIZ and national projects.
